{"tid":550052,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有冇人記得一家之鼠？","createTime":"2018-02-04T10:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-05T05:08:14.000Z","uid":121168,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d04c5379c0434f27ba21d33b582f31254cf572ee","tid":550052,"uid":121168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"超力仔算係童年一部好鐘意既戲。小學果陣代課，啲老師都好鐘意揀一家之鼠黎播比我地睇。以前電視明珠台成日都會播，我仲會追黎睇。不過好似已經好耐冇見電視播過。同類型既戲黎講，其實到而家都冇邊套深刻得過超力仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/183036_3493e0070b5104aef136492ee2987218.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F183036_3493e0070b5104aef136492ee2987218.png&h=3de47cc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dcd1ade38628c24232badeac0005f4312d36b25","tid":550052,"uid":4206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"想搵返粵語配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw以前有超力仔架跑車，不過後尾我整爛咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cfc030596bfe21b169a9013562d675445acd643","tid":550052,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"古巨基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c599893d9e81f70d2a4ab286cf0e94c9156654","tid":550052,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T13:42:44.000Z","msg":"最記得垃圾船砌飛機嗰幕"},{"pid":"0482236e83ab259ac98bd94db14dd0d259a8e6d8","tid":550052,"uid":4206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-04T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"最記得入面隻貓串個主人蠢到連屎同花生醬分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9676a507d72de9182a2ba5e268247ee0fdbb00fa","tid":550052,"uid":32672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"q